properties.comment_arrays: Array corrections from acquired image to radially distorted, in pixels
properties.comment_subchannel: number of the sensor port on a subcamera (0..2)
properties.comment_roll: lens rotation around the lens axis. Positive - CW looking to the target, degrees
properties.comment_subcamera: number of the subcamera with individual IP, starting with 0
properties.comment_channel: number of the sensor (channel) in the camera
properties.comment_azimuth: lens center azimuth, CW from top, degrees
properties.comment_elevation: lens elevation from horizontal, positive - above horizon, degrees
properties.comment_px0_py0: lens center on the sensor, in pixels
properties.comment_defects: Sensor hot/cold pixels list as x:y:difference
properties.comment_decimation: when decimation use integer divide to find the index, corection values are in non-decimated pixels
properties.comment_radius: lens center distance from the camera vertical axis, mm
properties.comment_height: lens center vertical position from the head center, mm
properties.comment_entrancePupilForward: entrance pupil distance from the azimuth/radius/height, outwards in mm
properties.comment_lensDistortionModel: Integer specifying lens distrotion model (0 - radial)
